ch.hsr.se2p.mrt.database
Class DatabaseHelper

java.lang.Object
  OrmLiteSqliteOpenHelper
      ch.hsr.se2p.mrt.database.DatabaseHelper

public class DatabaseHelper
extends OrmLiteSqliteOpenHelper

This class is responsible for managing the database. This means that it will create, upgrade or reset the database. Additionally, it is responsible to provide database access objects (or dao's, in short) to read from and write to the database.
